Figure 5 (A)

# Load the library
library(eulerr)
library(grid)
# Load the data
load("markers_lnvsf.RData")
nv_genes <- markers_l_nv$gene[markers_l_nv$cluster == "Mesenchymal_Alveolar"]
sf_genes <- markers_l_sf$gene[markers_l_sf$cluster == "Mesenchymal_Alveolar"]
shared <- length(intersect(nv_genes, sf_genes))
total_nv <- length(nv_genes)
total_sf <- length(sf_genes)
total <- total_nv + total_sf - shared  
data <- c(
  "Lung NV" = total_nv - shared, 
  "Lung SF" = total_sf - shared, 
  "Lung NV&Lung SF" = shared    
)
labels <- c(
  paste0(data["Lung NV"], "\n(", signif(data["Lung NV"] / total * 100, 4), "%)"), 
  paste0(data["Lung SF"], "\n(", signif(data["Lung SF"] / total * 100, 4), "%)"),  
  paste0(data["Lung NV&Lung SF"], "\n(", signif(data["Lung NV&Lung SF"] / total * 100, 4), "%)") 
)
# Show the figure
vennl1 <- euler(data)
vennl1<- plot(
  vennl1,
  fills = list(fill = c("#F9DF91", "#A8CFE8", "#E6D9AE"), alpha = 0.7),
  edges = NULL,
  labels = FALSE,
  main = list(label = "Mesenchymal_Alveolar", cex = 2.5, font = 2),
  quantities = FALSE 
)
vennl1
grid.text(labels[1], x = 0.14, y = 0.5, gp = gpar(fontsize = 20, fontface = "bold")) 
grid.text(labels[2], x = 0.86, y = 0.5, gp = gpar(fontsize = 20, fontface = "bold"))
grid.text(labels[3], x = 0.5, y = 0.5, gp = gpar(fontsize = 25, fontface = "bold"))

# Load the data
load("l_KEGG.RData")
# Show the figure
lnv_KEGG@compareClusterResult[["Description"]] <- gsub(" - Mus musculus \\(house mouse\\)", "", lnv_KEGG@compareClusterResult[["Description"]])
lsf_KEGG@compareClusterResult[["Description"]] <- gsub(" - Mus musculus \\(house mouse\\)", "", lsf_KEGG@compareClusterResult[["Description"]])
y_axis_order <- union(top_nv$Description, top_sf$Description)
x_axis_order <- c("Epithelial_Airway","Epithelial_Alveolar","Endothelial_Main", 
                  "Endothelial_Capillary", "Immune_Lymphoid", 
                  "Immune_Myeloid", "Mesenchymal_Airway/Vascular",
                  "Mesenchymal_Alveolar", "Mesenchymal_Pleura")
p1 <- enrichplot::dotplot(lnv_KEGG,x = "cluster",
                          color = "p.adjust",
                          font.size = 18,
                          showCategory = 10,
                          label_format=40) + 
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 30, hjust = 1)) + 
  ggtitle("Lung NV") +
  scale_y_discrete(limits = y_axis_order) +
  scale_x_discrete(limits = x_axis_order) + 
  theme(legend.position = "none",
        plot.title = element_text(size = 32, face = "bold"),
        axis.text.x = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),
        axis.text.y = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),
        axis.title.x = element_blank(),
        legend.title = element_text(size = 23, face = "bold"), 
        legend.text = element_text(size = 22, face = "bold")  
  )
p2 <- dotplot(lsf_KEGG, x = "cluster",
              color = "p.adjust",
              font.size = 18,
              showCategory = 10,
              label_format=40) + 
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 30, hjust = 1)) + 
  ggtitle("Lung SF") +
  scale_y_discrete(limits = y_axis_order) +
  scale_x_discrete(limits = x_axis_order) + 
  theme(axis.text.y = element_blank(),
        axis.title.y = element_blank(),
        plot.title = element_text(size = 32, face = "bold"),
        axis.text.x = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),
        axis.title.x = element_blank(),
        legend.title = element_text(size = 23, face = "bold"), 
        legend.text = element_text(size = 22, face = "bold") 
  )
p<- p1 + p2+ plot_layout(ncol = 2, widths = c(1, 1))
p

# Load the library
library(CellChat)
library(ggprism)
# Load the data
load("cellchat_l.RData")
par(mar = c(2, 2, 2, 2))
par(mfrow = c(1, 2), xpd = TRUE)
netVisual_circle(cellchat_lnv@net$count, vertex.weight = groupSize_nv,
                 weight.scale = TRUE, label.edge = FALSE,
                 vertex.label.cex = 0.8, vertex.label.color = "black",
                 title.name = "Lung NV")
netVisual_circle(cellchat_lsf@net$count, vertex.weight = groupSize_sf,
                 weight.scale = TRUE, label.edge = FALSE,
                 vertex.label.cex = 0.8, vertex.label.color = "black",
                 title.name = "Lung SF")

# Load the data
object.list <- list("Lung NV" = cellchat_lnv, "Lung SF" = cellchat_lsf)
cellchat <- mergeCellChat(object.list, add.names = names(object.list))
# Show the figure
compareInteractions(cellchat, show.legend = F, group = c(1,2))+ 
  theme_prism(base_size = 12) +
  guides(
    fill = guide_legend(
      title.theme = element_text(size = 13, face = "bold"),
      label.theme = element_text(size = 13, face = "bold")
    )
  ) + 
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 25, hjust = 1, vjust = 1),
    legend.position = "none" 
  )

Figure 5 (D)

import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')
import stereo as st
import pickle
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from matplotlib.patches import Rectangle
import os
# Load the data
class SafeUnpickler(pickle.Unpickler):
    def find_class(self, module, name):
        if module == 'stereo.core.result' and name == 'Result':
            class DummyResult(dict):
                def __setitem__(self, key, value):
                    super().__setitem__(key, value)
            return DummyResult
        return super().find_class(module, name)
file_path = 'Lung_NVSF.pkl'
with open(file_path, 'rb') as f:
   data= SafeUnpickler(f).load()
cell_names = data.cells.cell_name
platforms = [name.split('_')[0].split(' ')[1] for name in cell_names]
data.cells['platform'] = platforms
lnv_cells = data.cells[data.cells['platform'] == 'NV'].index.tolist()
lsf_cells = data.cells[data.cells['platform'] == 'SF'].index.tolist()
data_lnv = data.tl.filter_cells(cell_list=lnv_cells, inplace=False)
data_lsf = data.tl.filter_cells(cell_list=lsf_cells, inplace=False)
hs = data.tl.result['spatial_hotspot']
module_scores = hs.module_scores
lnv_module_scores = module_scores.loc[lnv_cells, :]
lsf_module_scores = module_scores.loc[lsf_cells, :]
data_lnv.tl.result['spatial_hotspot'].module_scores = lnv_module_scores
data_lsf.tl.result['spatial_hotspot'].module_scores = lsf_module_scores
# Show the figure
res = data_lnv.tl.result['spatial_hotspot']
module_id = 1
scores = res.module_scores[module_id]
coords = data_lnv.cells_matrix['spatial']
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 5))
sc = plt.scatter(
    coords[:, 0],
    coords[:, 1],
    c=scores,
    cmap="RdYlBu_r",
    s=5,
    vmin=-2,
    vmax=3.5
)
ax = plt.gca()
ax.invert_yaxis()
ax.set_aspect('equal')
ax.set_xticks([]);
ax.set_yticks([]);
for spine in ax.spines.values():
    spine.set_visible(False) 
cbar = plt.colorbar(sc,shrink=0.4, aspect=17)
cbar.set_ticks([-1, 0, 1, 2, 3])
plt.axis("off");
plt.title(f"module{module_id} Lung NV")
plt.show()

# Show the figure
res = data_lsf.tl.result['spatial_hotspot']
module_id = 1
scores = res.module_scores[module_id]
coords = data_lsf.cells_matrix['spatial']
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 5))
sc = plt.scatter(
    coords[:, 0],
    coords[:, 1],
    c=scores,
    cmap="RdYlBu_r",
    s=5,
    vmin=-2,
    vmax=3.5
)
ax = plt.gca()
ax.invert_yaxis()
ax.set_aspect('equal')
ax.set_xticks([]);
ax.set_yticks([]);
for spine in ax.spines.values():
    spine.set_visible(False) 
cbar = plt.colorbar(sc,shrink=0.4, aspect=17)
cbar.set_ticks([-1, 0, 1, 2, 3])
plt.axis("off");
plt.title(f"module{module_id} Lung SF")
plt.show()

# Load the library
library(SingleCellExperiment)
library(SpatialExperiment)
library(SVP)
# Load the data
load("Lung_gbv.RData")
spe <- SpatialExperiment(
  assays = list(logcounts = mat),
  spatialCoords = coords_avg
)
features <- as.vector(t(outer(paste0("module", 1:19), c("_NV","_SF"), paste0)))
features

## [11] "module6_NV"  "module6_SF"  "module7_NV"  "module7_SF"  "module8_NV"
